### 1. Sign in and copy accessToken to @token above
POST {{host}}/Auth/sign-in
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 2. Authorized request should work before logout
GET {{host}}/Tasks/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Logout revokes current token
POST {{host}}/Auth/logout
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Same token should now return 401 Unauthorized
GET {{host}}/Tasks/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
